long_description: furrever pet photography was first established back in 1999. 22 years and 3 owners later... animal lovers and fur parents to 9yo lab cross jet and 5yo english staffy indy. sick of working long hours for other business's only to live week to week, we quit our jobs and hit the ground running as a small business owners. after years of working in retail management and juggling casual photography related jobs, steph landed a full time role with a school/kinder photography company which helped develop her skills. alongside our family bookings, furrever pet photography also work with pet stores and vets across melbourne photographing their puppy school graduates, events & the ever so popular santa paws. furrever pet photography is a mornington peninsula based pet photography business. pets are our passion but we love to include everyone. our aim is to create life long memories for you at affordable prices. we want to capture the essence of you & your furry friend.
